data.title: Francis Folger “Franky” Franklin (1732
data.meta_description: Died at age 4 from Smallpox. 6/19/2019 Contributor (48521775) states  picture on Francis Franklin's memorial record has nothing to do with him. It is a screenshot of Minecraft.  I provide his comments for information only as I didn't post the pic, nor do I know this to be a fact. vrp 03/23/2020 Contributor Census taker...
